eaderlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h2><p><strong>本文未经允许，禁止转载！</strong></p><p><strong>视频教程正在制作，等待更新。</strong></p><h2 id=\"文章目录\"><a href=\"#文章目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文章目录\"></a>文章目录</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://blog.yfun.top/posts/hexo-blog/install-git\">安装 Git</a></li><li><a href=\"https://blog.yfun.top/posts/hexo-blog/install-nodejs\">安装 Node.js</a></li></ul><blockquote><p>更多文章等待更新...</p></blockquote><h2 id=\"下载\"><a href=\"#下载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载\"></a>下载</h2><p>前往 Node.js 官网 (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://node.js.org/\">https://node.js.org</a>)</p><p><picture><source class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/image-20220114174925675.webp\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" type=\"image/webp\"><img webp-comp=\"\" src=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/image-20220114174925675.png\" class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/image-20220114174925675.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" alt=\"image-20220114174925675\"></picture></p><p>下载 Node.js 安装包（推荐下载 LTS 版本）</p><p><picture><source class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175645.webp\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" type=\"image/webp\"><img webp-comp=\"\" src=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175645.png\" class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175645.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" alt=\"image-20220114175645642\"></picture></p><h2 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装\"></a>安装</h2><p>双击运行安装文件。</p><p>点击 <code>Next</code>。</p><p><picture><source class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175750.webp\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" type=\"image/webp\"><img webp-comp=\"\" src=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175750.png\" class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175750.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" alt=\"image-20220114175749822\"></picture></p><p>勾选同意协议，点击 <code>Next</code>。</p><p><picture><source class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175835.webp\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" type=\"image/webp\"><img webp-comp=\"\" src=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175835.png\" class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175835.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" alt=\"image-20220114175835742\"></picture></p><p>修改文件安装位置，点击 <code>Next</code>。（也可以不用改）</p><p><picture><source class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175929.webp\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" type=\"image/webp\"><img webp-comp=\"\" src=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175929.png\" class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114175929.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" alt=\"image-20220114175929226\"></picture></p><p>点击 <code>Next</code>。</p><p><picture><source class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180010.webp\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" type=\"image/webp\"><img webp-comp=\"\" src=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180010.png\" class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180010.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" alt=\"image-20220114180010036\"></picture></p><p><picture><source class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180044.webp\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" type=\"image/webp\"><img webp-comp=\"\" src=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180044.png\" class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180044.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" alt=\"image-20220114180043895\"></picture></p><p>点击 <code>Install</code> 开始安装。</p><p><picture><source class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180108.webp\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" type=\"image/webp\"><img webp-comp=\"\" src=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180108.png\" class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180108.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" alt=\"image-20220114180107827\"></picture></p><p>等待安装完成。<picture><source class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180122.webp\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" type=\"image/webp\"><img webp-comp=\"\" src=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180122.png\" class=\"lazyload-img\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.zhimg.com/ocoke-osg@0.0.14/rawimg/20220114180122.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAID/AP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs\" alt=\"image-20220114180122728\"></picture></p><p>点击 <code>Finish</code> 完成安装。</p><p><picture><source class=\